---
title: Sticky Glazed Halloumi and Chipotle Pilaf with Caramelised Onion, Peas and Soured Cream
description: Our Sticky Glazed Halloumi and Chipotle Pilaf is a delicious veggie option that makes it easy to eat more veg in your diet and try something new!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R22_W14_UK_V20379-3_Main_low-599ee401.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/65b9025cd1da3988cdd8dbc1.pdf
nutrition:
  calories: 906 kcal
  fat: 45.4 g
  saturated fat: 26.3 g
  carbohydrates: 91 g
  sugar: 20.9 g
